    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462260/extras/e42bd43a42c0280d3642669df05418b6.poster.avif?t=1744627770\" width=616 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462260/extras/e42bd43a42c0280d3642669df05418b6.webm?t=1744627770\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462260/extras/e42bd43a42c0280d3642669df05418b6.mp4?t=1744627770\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《Guild of Dragons》是一款具有驯龙、探索和征服元素的定居点建设游戏。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462260/extras/4b9d330c4e43267cc64feeb88c7e3939.avif?t=1744627770\" width=616 height=232 /></span><br><br>作为一名驭龙法师，你以第一人称视角养龙、探索、经营农场、制作物品和战斗，但在建设活动中采用自上而下的视角。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462260/extras/466cdeb3ac93879b45231f1ef9ea6768.avif?t=1744627770\" width=616 height=232 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>龙需要关注！</strong></h2>养育、喂养和驯服龙以便能够指挥和骑乘它们，否则它们可能会变成野龙并离开你！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462260/extras/50fc1c85640399e14fcccd586892868b.avif?t=1744627770\" width=616 height=232 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你和你的居民</strong></h2>扩大定居点的关键在于拥有足够的人手来为新建筑物配备人员。但在发生物资短缺时，你总是可以亲自上场（以第一人称视角）。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462260/extras/ea1ae96286b46a54b4efce20cfcc5434.avif?t=1744627770\" width=616 height=230 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>生产链</strong></h2>游戏中有各种各样的建筑物和生产链，可帮助你的定居点繁荣发展。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462260/extras/562a7caa133a847b7e04d0f5a9374ceb.avif?t=1744627770\" width=616 height=232 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>建设活动</strong></h2>虽然你是以第一人称或第三人称视角参与本游戏，但在进行建设活动时你将会转为自上而下的视角。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462260/extras/2ddbaf65c230d59fc8e8b550caccc6da.avif?t=1744627770\" width=616 height=232 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>贸易</strong></h2>与不同的商人进行交易，每个商人提供不同的商品。<br>根据他们与定居点的距离及其专业化程度，这些商人的商品买卖价格可能会有很大差异。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462260/extras/12539e6ec06b66f536b6ec5b2d9ae53f.avif?t=1744627770\" width=616 height=232 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>农场</strong></h2>从火龙果、农作物、花卉和草药等各式种植物之中进行选择，然后将它们种到温室、草药屋或农场中。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462260/extras/32a51be24279fe562a8d6d9f9239ec32.avif?t=1744627770\" width=616 height=232 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>采矿和制作</strong></h2>制作武器、药水和强化道具可为你的龙和你自己带来决定性的优势。当然，你必须先建造合适的建筑物。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462260/extras/ed4603050741c9708d4679b55edbd695.avif?t=1744627770\" width=616 height=232 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>怪物</strong></h2>《Guild of Dragons》中有各种各样的怪物有待发现。<br>但要注意，稀有资源通常会有怪物守护，所以你最好带上自己的龙之团队来确保安全。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462260/extras/cfd03794399e0a916ee16e253b238a50.avif?t=1744627770\" width=616 height=232 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>扩大你的领土</strong></h2>并带领你的龙之团队对抗残忍的德拉布集团的爪牙。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462260/extras/e2eba5ce3a2a74c72a989774d964a5e8.avif?t=1744627770\" width=616 height=232 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>德拉布集团</strong></h2>你的敌人——在他们不断扩大的势力范围内，利用恐惧来统治许多定居点。远古龙蛋散布在不同的地点，由德拉布怪鼠和怪物守卫。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462260/extras/29fe7150997b103adb45220fc384d4e4.avif?t=1744627770\" width=616 height=232 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>还有更多精彩内容</strong></h2><strong>任务</strong><br>你既可以体验更接近开放世界的风格，也可以跟随我们的主任务线，怎样游玩完全取决于你自己。<br><br><strong>用你自己的方式游玩——技能</strong><br>塑造你的角色并为你的龙选定发展道路，创造专属于你的体验！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462260/extras/ed7a962b22db41023bdc0a0b452f4e01.avif?t=1744627770\" width=616 height=232 /></span><br><br><strong>你的选择至关重要</strong><br>为了实现蓬勃发展，你需要支持自己的人民，但并非每个人都会对你的决定感到满意。你每做出一个决定都会有随之而来的代价。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462260/extras/ae304bc1104629e78ae54ec315d6ddcf.avif?t=1744627770\" width=616 height=232 /></span><br><br><strong>季节和天气</strong><br>《Guild of Dragons》采用了动态光照的昼夜循环机制。一些稀有植物只能在夜间发现和收集。<br>《Guild of Dragons》中也有分明的季节，农作物并非全年都可以生长。为了熬过严冬，你的人民和龙依赖于你储存的食物或贸易。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1462260/extras/6461254a64e31ae91c97c54487c4ac21.avif?t=1744627770\" width=616 height=232 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>剧情</strong></h2>维持世界平衡的巨龙早已不复存在，而驭龙法师的下落也仍然是个谜。<br><br>由此产生的权力真空被残忍的德拉布集团所填补。在他们的凶残领袖沙杜姆的领导下，德拉布集团建立起了一个恐怖国度。<br><br>四原色的使用被严令禁止，只剩下极少数原色驾驭者还在不断遭到猎杀和奴役。<br><br>原来，你才是唯一有能力用魔法来孵化和养育龙的人。<br><br>因此，作为最后也是最大的希望，只有你能建立一个美丽而神奇的世界，让龙族和人类再次繁荣昌盛！<br>- - -<br>",
